{{Use British English|date=February 2018}}
{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2018}}
'''Instant payment''' is a new way to exchange money and purchase services in seconds. Compared with [[wire transfer]]s they allow the transfer of money from the payer bank account to the payee bank account almost immediately, instead of requiring few business days. 
These payment systems have been developed (and are currently under development) worldwide as the need of faster and reliable transaction is the new economy common requirement.

The [[Euro Retail Payments Board]] (ERPB) has provided a widely accepted definition of '''instant payments''', that are: ''"electronic retail payment solutions available 24/7/365 and resulting in the immediate or close-to-immediate interbank clearing of the transaction and crediting of the payee’s account with confirmation to the payer (within seconds of payment initiation)."'' <ref name="definition">{{cite web |url=https://www.ecb.europa.eu/paym/retpaym/instant/html/index.en.html |title=Instant payments definition |publisher=European Central Bank |year=2017 |website=www.ecb.europa.eu |access-date=September 8, 2018}}</ref>

== Background ==
The growth of [[e-commerce]] has caused changes in people's spending patterns. Shopping is no longer confined to regular business hours, creating a new challenges for funds transfers.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bancaditalia.it/pubblicazioni/interventi-governatore/integov2017/Visco_30112017.pdf |title=Digital transformation of the retail payments ecosystem|page=3 |publisher=Banca d'Italia |date=November 30, 2017 |website=www.bancaditalia.it |access-date=September 2, 2018}}</ref> 
Similarly, merchants require faster and more reliable money transfer systems to keep up with consumer demand.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instapay.today/instant-payments/ |title=What are instant payments? |publisher=InstaPay |year=2018 |website=www.instapay.today |access-date=September 2, 2018}}</ref>

Traditional electronic payments like [[wire transfer]]s, that perform the [[electronic funds transfer]] within few business days, are not in line with user expectations. 
It is predicted{{By whom|date=September 2018}} that in the next year instant payments will become the standard for electronic fund transfers.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://insights.nordea.com/instant-payments-are-future-heres-why |title=Instant payments are the future - here’s why |publisher=Nordea |year=2018 |website=insights.nordea.com |access-date=September 2, 2018}}</ref>

